# SCP Survivor Licensing Overview / 许可总览

This repository contains materials under more than one license. 本仓库包含适用不同许可证的材料。

1. Independently authored software code / 独立软件代码
   Unless otherwise noted, independently authored software code remains available under the MIT License. The complete text is in `LICENSES/MIT.txt`.
   除非另有说明，独立创作的软件代码继续按 MIT License 提供；完整文本见 `LICENSES/MIT.txt`。
2. SCP-derived content / SCP 衍生内容
   Content relating to the SCP Foundation, SCP-049, and other SCP-derived creative expression is provided under CC BY-SA 3.0, subject to the final project licensing review. The complete text is in `LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-3.0.txt`; attribution is in `ATTRIBUTION.md`.
   与 SCP Foundation、SCP-049 及其他 SCP 衍生创意表达有关的内容，在项目最终许可复核通过的前提下按 CC BY-SA 3.0 提供；完整文本见 `LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-3.0.txt`，署名见 `ATTRIBUTION.md`。
3. Project-generated assets / 项目生成素材
   Source and modification records are listed in `docs/art/asset-register.md`. Inclusion here is not a warranty of uniqueness, non-infringement, or commercial-release clearance.
   来源与修改记录见 `docs/art/asset-register.md`。纳入本仓库不构成对唯一性、不侵权或商业发布许可已经完备的保证。

This overview preserves rights already granted for earlier MIT-licensed code copies and is not legal advice. 该总览不撤回既有 MIT 代码副本已经获得的权利，也不构成法律意见。
